875
00:35:13,260 --> 00:35:15,060
Don't worry about the tuition.

876
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:16,940
We offer financial aid.

877
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:19,980
If Qu Zhen works hard enough,

878
00:35:20,380 --> 00:35:21,860
