879
00:35:22,420 --> 00:35:23,220
And

880
00:35:23,820 --> 00:35:25,180
we have dormitories.

881
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,740
You can live here without any cost.

882
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:28,900
We can study here

883
00:35:28,900 --> 00:35:30,100
without paying tuition.

884
00:35:30,740 --> 00:35:31,340
Really?

885
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:33,180
Ms. Zhuang, can we really

886
00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:34,140
study here

887
00:35:34,140 --> 00:35:34,900
for free?

888
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:37,300
Yes.

889
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:40,380
Thank Ms. Zhuang now.

890
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:41,780
Thank you, Ms. Zhuang.

891
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:43,380
- Thank you.
- Thank you, Ms. Zhuang.

892
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,140
No problem.

893
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,700
But there is one condition.

894
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:46,820
What is it?

895
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:49,020
If you pass the exam tomorrow,

896
00:35:49,540 --> 00:35:50,980
you can study here for free.

897
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:52,060
What's on the exam?

898
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:54,820
What dance moves can you do now?

899
00:35:55,140 --> 00:35:56,340
How long can you hold them?

900
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:01,020
I don't know. I've never counted.

901
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:03,220
But they're probably not very standard.

902
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:05,700
I can give you

903
00:36:06,300 --> 00:36:07,300
a special training session tonight.

904
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,100
You seem

905
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:19,580
preoccupied.

906
00:36:24,580 --> 00:36:25,140
No.

907
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:28,340
Honestly,

908
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:30,100
I just said it offhand

909
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:31,540
that day.

910
00:36:32,140 --> 00:36:33,220
If you've changed your mind,

911
00:36:33,860 --> 00:36:34,820
there's still time.

912
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:36,020
How could I?

913
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:38,060
Have you told Le?

914
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:40,500
Tell Le?

915
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:42,940
About us.

916
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:47,500
Should we tell him?

917
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:48,020
I...

918
00:36:48,620 --> 00:36:49,620
I haven't decided yet.

919
00:36:49,900 --> 00:36:50,540
Maybe

920
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:52,780
we should

921
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:54,420
try things out first?

922
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:57,860
Sounds like you're the one
having a hard time with it.

923
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:01,180
I am having a hard time with it.

924
00:37:01,460 --> 00:37:02,580
From now on, I'll be

925
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,820
a free piano teacher and nanny.

926
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,220
You're getting quite the deal.

927
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:09,140
Le will be so happy.

928
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:12,860
I hope he is happy too.

929
00:37:14,300 --> 00:37:15,940
I'll come to your place often

930
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:17,580
to take care of him.

931
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:19,980
And

932
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:21,820
look after you too.

933
00:37:50,940 --> 00:37:51,500
Do you like it?

934
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:52,980
Yes.

935
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,140
I loved it too

936
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:55,860
the first time I saw a dance studio

937
00:37:55,900 --> 00:37:56,780
as a child.

938
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:03,700
Madam, can I really learn ballet here?

939
00:38:04,340 --> 00:38:05,420
As long as you truly like it

940
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:06,740
and are willing, you can.

941
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,340
Alright.

942
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,260
You can stand like that

943
00:38:16,260 --> 00:38:17,380
thanks to your natural

944
00:38:17,620 --> 00:38:18,340
physical strength.

945
00:38:18,860 --> 00:38:20,180
It's normal you can't hold it for long.

946
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:21,780
Because you haven't had
professional training.

947
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:23,980
When we practice

948
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:25,060
working on pointe,

949
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:26,420
we rely on the shoe's support

950
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:28,820
and strong ankle strength.

951
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:30,700
But don't worry.

952
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,940
This isn't on tomorrow's exam.

953
00:38:33,060 --> 00:38:34,420
I can teach you something useful.

954
00:38:34,620 --> 00:38:36,460
Some tips for the basic moves.

955
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:37,700
Okay, Madam.

956
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:38,620
They're easy to learn.

957
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,820
Place your hands on the barre.

958
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,260
Feet together.

959
00:38:43,100 --> 00:38:44,020
Get up on demi-pointe.

960
00:38:45,580 --> 00:38:46,100
Can you do it?

961
00:38:50,260 --> 00:38:50,820
Get up.

962
00:38:51,060 --> 00:38:52,140
Head up a little.

963
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:53,500
Shoulders down.

964
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:55,020
Heels pressing down.

965
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:21,260
Very good.

966
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,140
Hands back a bit.

967
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:24,900
That's good.

968
00:39:25,300 --> 00:39:27,220
One, two, three, down.

969
00:39:36,300 --> 00:39:37,060
Tired?

970
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,140
Take a break.

971
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:40,140
You should be fine

972
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:41,220
if you

973
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:43,260
do this tomorrow. Don't be nervous.

974
00:39:44,460 --> 00:39:47,020
Ms. Tan, you're so kind to me.
Thank you.

975
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:50,660
I just want to protect
your original love for ballet.

976
00:39:51,940 --> 00:39:52,540
Original love?

977
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:55,300
Old Sir said he hopes I can always dance

978
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:57,300
listening to the voice in my heart.

979
00:39:57,660 --> 00:39:58,660
Is it the same meaning?

980
00:40:01,580 --> 00:40:02,380
Pretty much.

981
00:40:03,540 --> 00:40:04,780
I definitely will.

982
00:40:05,100 --> 00:40:07,060
I love ballet the most.

983
00:40:07,180 --> 00:40:08,380
Before I met Old Sir,

984
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:11,060
my favorite was the dancing
from back home.

985
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:12,420
After I met him,

986
00:40:12,420 --> 00:40:14,100
ballet became my favorite.

987
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:15,700
I heard you say

988
00:40:16,740 --> 00:40:18,940
Old Sir is an elder from your village.

989
00:40:20,220 --> 00:40:22,100
People from my village

990
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,580
go to him with all their problems.

991
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:25,580
He's a very reliable person.

992
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:29,780
Ms. Tan, thank you so much.

993
00:40:29,860 --> 00:40:32,620
Back home, we dance when we're happy.

994
00:40:32,860 --> 00:40:34,020
And I'm very happy right now.

995
00:40:34,020 --> 00:40:35,580
Can I dance?

996
00:40:35,620 --> 00:40:36,500
Of course.

997
00:40:52,660 --> 00:40:53,100
It's OK.

998
00:40:54,180 --> 00:40:54,980
Did you get the phone number?

999
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:55,380
Hey!

1000
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:56,540
Want to learn about the Volleyball Club?

1001
00:40:57,580 --> 00:40:58,300
Next one.

1002
00:41:01,940 --> 00:41:02,380
Next one.

1003
00:41:11,100 --> 00:41:11,460
Hello.

1004
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:12,860
It's you.

1005
00:41:13,300 --> 00:41:14,340
The ride-sharing driver.

1006
00:41:14,540 --> 00:41:16,180
I'm your savior
who found your dance shoes

1007
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:18,100
and saved your career.

1008
00:41:19,740 --> 00:41:21,100
You know each other?

1009
00:41:21,980 --> 00:41:22,900
The day of my Queen Ballet audition,

1010
00:41:23,060 --> 00:41:24,780
he took a shortcut when driving me.

1011
00:41:24,900 --> 00:41:25,660
If it weren't for him,

1012
00:41:25,780 --> 00:41:26,700
I would have been finished.

1013
00:41:27,100 --> 00:41:27,940
I remember you telling me that story.

1014
00:41:28,340 --> 00:41:29,220
What a coincidence.

1015
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:30,940
You want to learn ballet?

1016
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:32,380
Just passing by.

1017
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:34,260
And I saw someone I know.

1018
00:41:35,220 --> 00:41:36,180
Your savior.

1019
00:41:36,580 --> 00:41:37,260
Want to sign up?

1020
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:37,940
Can I?

1021
00:41:38,020 --> 00:41:39,540
I'm quite interested in ballet.

1022
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:40,940
Is that not allowed?

1023
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:43,340
Can I?

1024
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:45,460
Sure.

1025
00:41:46,380 --> 00:41:47,500
Fill out this form.

1026
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:48,820
Tomorrow, 9 AM,

1027
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:49,900
at the ballet studio.

1028
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:51,420
But let's make it clear.

1029
00:41:51,500 --> 00:41:52,540
I'm very strict.

1030
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,220
I'm afraid you might not keep up.

1031
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:55,820
No problem.

1032
00:41:56,420 --> 00:41:57,340
I like being treated strictly.

1033
00:42:26,740 --> 00:42:27,460
