I'm... I'm practicing.

1035
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:30,980
Ouch, ouch!

1036
00:42:30,980 --> 00:42:31,580
Practice a bit longer.

1037
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:32,220
No more. I'm done.

1038
